      "title": "A pound of bread costs Rs 300",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Due to the shortage of wheat flour in the market, the price of a pound of bread is currently being sold at a price between Rs 250-300. However, most of the bakeries have now stopped producing bread.",
        "Due to the shortage of wheat flour in the market, the price of bread has increased significantly."
